Package: chivy
Version: 0.5
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Section: games
Depends: python (>= 2.6), python-rabbyt (>= 0.8.1), python-pyglet (>= 1.1.2)
Maintainer: Micha≈Ç Sapalski <sapalskimichal@gmail.com>
Description: Simple multiplayer action game with logic elements.
 It requires of players high attention divisibility, skillful hands and 
 quick thinking.  Chivy can be played by many players on one computer 
 (up to 4 players), through network or with computer opponents 
 (6 difficulty levels). 
 There are some levels included, but it is also possible to generate 
 a random board.
